These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-3-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, tea, fanta, almond-milk, mirinda, soy-milk
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
7. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
9. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |  3   |   4    |    5     |    6     |  7  |
| Beverage   | mirinda | fanta | hot-chocolate | soy-milk | almond-milk | tea | coffee |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-3-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  software-developer, lawyer, dancer, architect, writer, teacher, entrepreneur
1. the teacher is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
2. the lawyer is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
3. the software-developer is on the right of the writer##1
4. the teacher is on the far right##1
5. the entrepreneur is on the left or right of the architect##3
6. the architect is on the left of the writer##1
7. the architect is on the left of the writer##1
8. the lawyer is between the entrepreneur and the dancer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |    2     |      3       |      4      |      5       |  6   |   7   |
| Job   | dancer | lawyer | entrepreneur | architect | writer | software-developer | teacher |

