.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-3-3::.
There are 7 different nationalities: pakistani, malaysian, mexican, nigerian, polish, egyptian, italian
1. the malaysian is on the far left or far right##3
2. the pakistani is between the malaysian and the polish##2
3. the polish is on the right of the pakistani##1
4. the pakistani is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
5. the italian is on the left of the egyptian##1
6. the italian is between the mexican and the egyptian##2
7. the egyptian is on the left or right of the nigerian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |     4      |    5    |   6    |    7     |
| Nationality   | malaysian | pakistani | polish | mexican | italian | egyptian | nigerian |

