.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-3-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: ambient, punk, electronic, techno, d&b, folk, trance
1. the fan of electronic is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
2. the fan of d&b is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
3. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of punk##1
4. the fan of trance is on the right of the fan of folk##1
5. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of techno##1
6. the fan of d&b is in the middle##1
7. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |   2    |    3    |  4  |   5   |    6    |    7    |
| Music-Genre   | folk | trance | ambient | d&b | techno | electronic | punk |

