.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-3-5::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: drawing, singing, woodworking, chess, video-games, board-games, sudoku
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |      3      |    4    |       5       |    6    |    7    |
| Hobby   | video-games | singing | chess | sudoku | board-games | woodworking | drawing |

