6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left##1
7. the owner of the pony is in the middle##1
8. the owner of the frog is on the far right##1
9. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |  2  |  3   |   4    |   5   |   6    |   7   |
