.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-3-20::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: reggae, gospel, electronic, techno, blues, country, disco
1. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
2. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
3. the fan of gospel is on the far right##1
4. the fan of gospel is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
5. the fan of blues is between the fan of electronic and the fan of disco##2
6. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of blues##1
7. the fan of electronic is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
8. the fan of techno is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2  |  3  |   4   |  5   |     6     |    7    |
| Music-Genre   | techno | country | disco | blues | electronic | reggae | gospel |

 